  - Latency: 10 μs read, 20 μs write
  - Endurance: 30,000 write cycles
  
• Secondary Storage: 3D NAND Flash
  - Capacity: 500 TB
  - Bandwidth: 5 GB/s read, 2 GB/s write
  - Latency: 100 μs read, 500 μs write
  - Endurance: 10,000 write cycles

• Archive Storage: Quantum Holographic
  - Capacity: 1 PB (per satellite)
  - Bandwidth: 1 GB/s read, 100 MB/s write
  - Latency: 10 ms
  - Retention: >10,000 years
```

