9.2 Navigation System

```
NAVIGATION SENSORS:

STAR TRACKERS (4×):
• Field of View: 20° × 20°
• Accuracy: 0.0001° (0.36 arcseconds)
• Update Rate: 10 Hz
• Magnitude Limit: +6.0
